--[Patch]--
Title("Disable Music")
Author("Hyper")
Platform("All Systems")
Blurb("Disables all in-game and cutscene music.")
Description("This patch will disable all music tracks. This may only be useful to Xbox 360 players, since the game doesn't save audio settings on that version.")

--[Functions]--
Xbox 360:
RenameByExtension("core\sound"|"*.xma"|".xma_back")
RenameByExtension("core\sound\event"|"*.xma"|".xma_back")

PlayStation 3:
RenameByExtension("core\sound"|"*.at3"|".at3_back")
RenameByExtension("core\sound\event"|"*.at3"|".at3_back")